[2] R. Santos, J. P. Matos-Carvalho, S. Tomic and M. Beko, "WLS algorithm for UAV navigation in satellite‚Äêless environments," in IET Wireless Sensor Systems, 2022, 12, (3-4), p. 93-102, DOI: 10.1049/wss2.12041
